  <brief_title>The Effect of Lansoprazole in Combination With Ecabet Sodium for Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial to Evaluate the Effect of Lansoprazole in Combination With Ecabet Sodium for Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
