  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We will estimate the responses of lansoprazole and ecabet sodium combination therapy and
      compare with lansoprazole and placebo therapy in patients who need additional therapy after
      standard proton pump inhibitor treatment for 4week or more in recurrent gastroesophageal
      reflux disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
